{"id":35,"parent_id":0,"book_id":80,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":35,"title":"Chapter 32: Captain Moroni and the Title of Liberty","subtitle":"","short_title":"Chapter 32","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"chapter","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.head1"},[".titleNumber","Chapter 32"],["h1","Captain Moroni and the Title of Liberty"]],[".bodyBlock",[".image",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f1"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_01.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p3"},"A wicked man named Amalickiah wanted to be king over the Nephites. Many Nephites had left the Church to follow him."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p4"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.1,4-5,7"},"Alma 46:1, 4–5, 7"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f2"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_02.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p5"},"If Amalickiah became king, he would try to destroy the Church of God and take away the people’s liberty."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p6"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.9-10"},"Alma 46:9–10"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f3","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f3"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_03.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p7"},"When Captain Moroni, the leader of the Nephite armies, heard of Amalickiah’s plan to be king, he became angry."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p8"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.11"},"Alma 46:11"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f4","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f4"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_04.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p9"},"Moroni tore his coat to make a flag. On it he wrote a message to remind the people to defend their religion, freedom, and peace."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p10"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.12"},"Alma 46:12"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f5","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f5"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_05.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p11"},"Moroni put the flag on a pole and called it the title of liberty. Then dressed in his armor, he knelt to pray."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.13"},"Alma 46:13"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f6","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f6"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_06.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p13","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p13"},"He asked God to protect those who believed in Jesus Christ and prayed for freedom in the land, calling it a land of liberty."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p14"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.16-18"},"Alma 46:16–18"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f7","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f7"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_07.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p15","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p15"},"Moroni went among the people. Waving the title of liberty, he called them to come and help protect their freedom."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.19-20"},"Alma 46:19–20"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f8","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f8"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_08.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p17"},"People came from all over the land. They promised to obey God’s commandments and to fight for freedom."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.21-22,28"},"Alma 46:21–22, 28"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f9","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f9"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_09.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p19"},"When Amalickiah saw how many Nephites had joined with Moroni, he was afraid. He and his followers left to join the Lamanites."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.29-30"},"Alma 46:29–30"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f10","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f10"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_10.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p21"},"Moroni and his army tried to stop them, but Amalickiah and a few of his men escaped."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p22","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p22"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.31-33"},"Alma 46:31–33"]]]],[".image",{"id":"f11","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.f11"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/gospel-library/manual/35666/35666_all_035_11.jpg"}],[".caption",["p.para",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p23"},"Moroni placed a title of liberty on every tower in the Nephite land. The Nephites had kept their freedom and again had peace."]],[".citationInfo",["p.para",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/book-of-mormon-stories/chapter-32-captain-moroni-and-the-title-of-liberty.p24"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/46.36-37"},"Alma 46:36–37"]]]]]]]],"refs":null}
